comments: Bullock (DAL) legally contests Bogdanovic's (DET) jump shot attempt.
Burks (DET) moves towards Doncic (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Doncic receives the pass.
Bogdanovic (DET) briefly grasps Bullock's (DAL) arm and marginal contact occurs as they engage for off-ball position.
Bullock (DAL) is moving alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Bey (DET) brings his off arm towards Green (DAL) and marginal contact occurs during Bey's drive.
Doncic (DAL) legally contests Bey's (DET) driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Duren (DET) during rebounding.
Burks (DET) turns slightly towards Dinwiddie's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs prior to Dinwiddie's gather.
Finney-Smith (DAL) holds Bogdanovic's (DET) arm and restricts his pursuit of the rebound.

Dinwiddie (DAL) brings his forearm towards Bogdanovic's (DET) front and immediately removes his arm as Bogdanovic begins his upward shooting motion.  Additionally, Dinwiddie's left hand/arm avoids making contact with Bogdanovic's right arm.
Green (DAL) loses control of the ball on his own, and any ensuing contact from Burks (DET) is marginal.
Finney-Smith (DAL) brings his left hand/arm forward and makes contact with Bogdanovic's (DET) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
After the loose ball is secured by Green (DAL), Bogdanovic (DET) trips over Green's body and marginal contact occurs after Green has passed the ball.
Bey (DET) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Bullock (DAL) and Stewart (DET) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
